Locus Robotics was founded in 2014 by a group of individuals including Bruce Welty, Dave Vos, Rick Faulk, and Mike Johnson. Bruce Welty is a veteran of the warehouse automation industry, Dave Vos is an experienced robotics engineer, Rick Faulk is a seasoned executive with experience in software and technology, and Mike Johnson is a robotics expert who has worked on various automation projects. The company provides autonomous mobile robots to help warehouse and distribution center operators improve efficiency and productivity.